36
00:03:25,490 --> 00:03:26,590
Okay!

37
00:03:26,990 --> 00:03:28,190
"8:20 pm, at the hotel"

38
00:03:28,190 --> 00:03:32,490
The victim is Chizuru Bizen, an actress, 30 years old.

39
00:03:32,490 --> 00:03:35,190
