57
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:27,090
I see.

58
00:04:27,090 --> 00:04:29,090
Hey, you!

59
00:04:29,090 --> 00:04:31,190
You can't go in there, sonny!

60
00:04:31,190 --> 00:04:32,790
But...

61
00:04:32,790 --> 00:04:34,990
That kid again!

62
00:04:36,290 --> 00:04:38,290
You just keep still, understand?

63
00:04:38,290 --> 00:04:41,190
