65
00:04:42,890 --> 00:04:45,690
That's the part that the metal part of the door guard used to be.

66
00:04:45,690 --> 00:04:48,490
There are strange scratches on the metal on the floor part too.

67
00:04:48,490 --> 00:04:50,590
These scratches could've been made

68
00:04:50,590 --> 00:04:54,590
