69
00:04:54,590 --> 00:04:56,890
What? What do you mean?

70
00:04:56,890 --> 00:05:00,690
In other words, after the killer locked the window,

71
00:05:00,690 --> 00:05:03,390
he probably used the screw driver

72
00:05:03,390 --> 00:05:05,390
to remove the door guard from the wall.

73
00:05:05,390 --> 00:05:07,990
Then he went out to the corridor from the door,

74
00:05:07,990 --> 00:05:10,090
