77
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:15,490
But since trying to screw the screw back on

78
00:05:15,490 --> 00:05:16,890
from such a narrow space was too difficult,

79
00:05:16,890 --> 00:05:19,990
the killer inadvertently left scratches in the vicinity.

80
00:05:19,990 --> 00:05:24,190
The metal part probably fell off in one blow at the door

81
00:05:24,190 --> 00:05:26,590
because the screw wasn't screwed on tightly enough.

82
00:05:27,590 --> 00:05:31,090
Officer, Chizuru moved this table from the window

83
00:05:31,090 --> 00:05:32,690
