84
00:05:32,690 --> 00:05:34,590
Yeah, that's right.

85
00:05:34,590 --> 00:05:36,490
Then...

86
00:05:36,490 --> 00:05:39,090
Don't bother the officer!

87
00:05:39,090 --> 00:05:42,090
Are there foot prints on the soles of the legs too?

88
00:05:42,090 --> 00:05:44,390
What? Of course!

89
00:05:44,390 --> 00:05:46,190
Why don't you check your feet...

90
00:05:46,190 --> 00:05:48,890
Wait! Chizuru had no shoes...

91
00:05:48,890 --> 00:05:51,090
Barefoot!

92
00:05:51,090 --> 00:05:54,590
Were Chizuru's footprints on the table?

93
00:05:54,590 --> 00:05:56,790
No!

94
00:05:56,790 --> 00:05:59,690
What? Which means that...

95
00:05:59,690 --> 00:06:03,190
Someone carried Chizuru up and hung her.

96
00:06:03,190 --> 00:06:06,190
Which means that this is homicide, not suicide.

97
00:06:06,190 --> 00:06:09,990
Last night, Chizuru was arguing with someone in the restaurant.

98
00:06:10,590 --> 00:06:13,690
Gosh. If only I had confirmed who it was back then...

99
00:06:15,290 --> 00:06:17,290
I wonder if there is no other evidence.

100
00:06:19,590 --> 00:06:20,790
What's this?

101
00:06:20,790 --> 00:06:23,290
There's some white and powdery.

102
00:06:24,690 --> 00:06:27,290
This room sure is hot.

103
00:06:28,590 --> 00:06:29,990
The air conditioner!

104
00:06:29,990 --> 00:06:33,190
It wasn't running since we found the corpse.

105
00:06:33,190 --> 00:06:36,890
Did the killer turn it off?

106
00:06:42,390 --> 00:06:45,790
I would like to ask you a few questions

107
00:06:45,790 --> 00:06:48,290
