112
00:06:55,490 --> 00:07:00,290
Well, the alimony she demanded was such a huge sum, so...

113
00:07:00,290 --> 00:07:01,690
I see.

114
00:07:01,690 --> 00:07:03,190
Next, Mr. Miyabe.

115
00:07:03,190 --> 00:07:05,090
I hear you wanted her to drop the star role

116
00:07:05,090 --> 00:07:07,290
