138
00:07:57,290 --> 00:07:59,290
I had lunch with Mr. Mouri

139
00:07:59,290 --> 00:08:01,990
and left the hotel at 1:30 pm.

140
00:08:01,990 --> 00:08:04,990
Did you see Chizuru then?

141
00:08:04,990 --> 00:08:08,990
I went to check on her as soon as I got back to the hotel,

142
00:08:08,990 --> 00:08:10,690
but since she didn't answer the door when I knocked,

143
00:08:10,690 --> 00:08:13,490
so I returned to the lobby.

144
00:08:13,490 --> 00:08:16,090
Which means that Mr. Miyabe, you were all alone

145
00:08:16,090 --> 00:08:19,190
while Mr. Shiromoto was back here at the hotel?

146
00:08:19,190 --> 00:08:21,190
Yes, of course.

147
00:08:21,190 --> 00:08:24,190
I was eating lunch at the lakeside.

148
00:08:24,990 --> 00:08:27,090
How about you two? Mr. Arimori and Shinobu?

149
00:08:27,090 --> 00:08:29,990
We went with Conan and Ran

150
00:08:29,990 --> 00:08:31,790
to the highlands at the top of the mountain.

151
00:08:31,790 --> 00:08:35,790
We left right after Mr. Shiromoto and Mr. Miyabe left,

152
00:08:35,790 --> 00:08:38,490
and arrived at the highlands around 11 am.

153
00:08:38,490 --> 00:08:40,590
We were there all through

154
00:08:40,590 --> 00:08:43,690
and started down at around 6 pm.

155
00:08:43,690 --> 00:08:46,390
We got back to the hotel around 7 pm.

156
00:08:46,390 --> 00:08:49,490
I hear only you, Mr. Arimori, remained at the highlands?

157
00:08:49,490 --> 00:08:53,190
The engine of my van wasn't functioning too well.

158
00:08:53,190 --> 00:08:56,490
When you went to pick him up, was Mr. Arimori there?

159
00:08:56,490 --> 00:08:57,890
Of course.

160
00:08:57,890 --> 00:09:01,390
I was with her, so there's no doubt about it.

161
00:09:01,390 --> 00:09:03,690
How about you two, Minaho and Honami?

162
00:09:03,690 --> 00:09:06,990
We were cleaning the hotel in the morning.

163
00:09:06,990 --> 00:09:09,390
Since Mr. Shiromoto came back

164
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:11,690
and started eating lunch with Mr. Mouri,

165
00:09:11,690 --> 00:09:13,190
we served them tea

166
00:09:13,190 --> 00:09:16,190
and went to have lunch in the office.

167
00:09:16,190 --> 00:09:19,690
After seeing Mr. Shiromoto off at 1:30 pm,

168
00:09:19,690 --> 00:09:23,090
we watched TV till 4 pm.

169
00:09:23,090 --> 00:09:25,790
After that, we were in the kitchen

170
00:09:25,790 --> 00:09:28,290
making preparations for dinner until everyone returned.

171
00:09:29,290 --> 00:09:30,490
When you did the cleaning,

172
00:09:30,490 --> 00:09:32,090
what did you do about Chizuru's room?

173
00:09:32,090 --> 00:09:35,490
The manager had told us not to disturb her, so...

174
00:09:35,490 --> 00:09:37,890
We didn't go near her room.

175
00:09:37,890 --> 00:09:40,190
Were you at the hotel right through, Mr. Mouri?

176
00:09:40,190 --> 00:09:43,890
Yes, I was watching TV in the lobby right through.

177
00:09:43,890 --> 00:09:48,090
After Mr. Shiromoto went to check on her at around 12:30 noon,

178
00:09:48,090 --> 00:09:50,790
nobody used the stairs by the lobby.

179
00:09:50,790 --> 00:09:51,790
Which means,

180
00:09:51,790 --> 00:09:55,590
the killer must've entered the hotel from the emergency exit.

181
00:09:55,590 --> 00:09:58,090
