245
00:12:29,990 --> 00:12:33,090
The white powder that was on Chizuru's skirt.

246
00:12:33,990 --> 00:12:35,890
What on earth was it?

247
00:12:36,990 --> 00:12:39,090
I see! Maybe...

248
00:12:45,190 --> 00:12:47,590
This is similar to a runway.

249
00:12:53,690 --> 00:12:55,190
What's that?

250
00:12:55,190 --> 00:12:57,190
It looks like a mark that was made by rope rubbing against the wall.

251
00:13:12,590 --> 00:13:14,790
Officer.

252
00:13:14,790 --> 00:13:17,590
Mr. Mouri told me to ask...

253
00:13:17,590 --> 00:13:19,090
What?

254
00:13:19,090 --> 00:13:20,990
So, I'd like you all, Mr. Shiromoto,

255
00:13:20,990 --> 00:13:24,990
Mr. Miyabe, Minaho, Honami, and Mr. Mouri

256
00:13:24,990 --> 00:13:26,590
to come to the station with me for more detailed questioning.

257
00:13:26,590 --> 00:13:29,990
Just who do you think I am anyway?

258
00:13:31,990 --> 00:13:33,490
Sleep is overtaking me.

259
00:13:34,490 --> 00:13:37,290
What's the matter, Mr. Mouri?

260
00:13:37,290 --> 00:13:41,290
Please wait! It's the beginning of the Sleeping Kogoro!

261
00:13:42,790 --> 00:13:45,690
What? So this is the rumored...

